<br>
I personally won't be going since my guild has determined that we'd stay. But I envy those of you who are. you basically get a clean start on new hardware, no lag, and free reign to do whatever <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> </font><P><b>Opafaf Darkenroot</b> <br>
